snippet.title: Commander Cherry's Puzzled Journey - PS4
snippet.description:
Make a photo of your body you can walk on! 
Welcome aboard, cadet! 
Help Commander Cherry on his adventure and get creative with your body! 

You play the game using the PlayStation®Camera and a your controller simultaneously. 

http://www.grande-games.com/
